    <entry>
      <title>前端倒计时插件leftTime</title>
      <link href="2020/12/30/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E5%80%92%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6leftTime/"/>
      <url>2020/12/30/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E5%80%92%E8%AE%A1%E6%97%B6%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6leftTime/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="lefttime前端倒计时插件的使用步骤"><a href="#lefttime前端倒计时插件的使用步骤" class="headerlink" title="lefttime前端倒计时插件的使用步骤"></a>lefttime前端倒计时插件的使用步骤</h2><a id="more"></a><p>​      倒计时插件只是定时的产生数字, 所以需要使用这个数字, 替换需要倒计时的文字</p><p>​      使用步骤:</p><h3 id="1-导入开发包"><a href="#1-导入开发包" class="headerlink" title="1, 导入开发包,"></a>1, 导入开发包,</h3><p>leftTime插件基于jquery, 所以要先加入jquery的开发包</p><pre class="line-numbers language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class="token attr-name">language</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>javascript<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">th:</span>src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>@{/js/jquery-1.7.2.min.js}<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span class="token script"></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">th:</span>src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>@{/js/leftTime.min.js}<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>text/javascript<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span class="token script"></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="2-准备容器-需要倒计时的文本"><a href="#2-准备容器-需要倒计时的文本" class="headerlink" title="2, 准备容器(需要倒计时的文本)"></a>2, 准备容器(需要倒计时的文本)</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class="token attr-name">id</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>msgCodeBtn<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>获取验证码<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="3-容器加载完毕后-对容器调用工具函数"><a href="#3-容器加载完毕后-对容器调用工具函数" class="headerlink" title="3, 容器加载完毕后, 对容器调用工具函数"></a>3, 容器加载完毕后, 对容器调用工具函数</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>text/javascript<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span class="token script"><span class="token language-javascript"><span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"#msgCodeBtn"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">click</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token comment">//$.leftTime(倒数时间, 处理函数(d){d封装了倒数的相关信息; 每次倒数时都会调用});</span>        $<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">leftTime</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">60</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">d</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>            <span class="token comment">//插件会生成自动倒数的数字 d.status=false时停止倒数, d.s剩余秒数最开始时会显示00</span>            <span class="token comment">//使用系统函数抽取整数部分, 将05转换为5</span>            <span class="token keyword">var</span> leftS <span class="token operator">=</span> window<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">parseInt</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>status<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>                <span class="token comment">//开始倒数时, 为按钮添加"on"样式, 使之变成灰色</span>                <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"#msgCodeBtn"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">addClass</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"on"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>                <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"#msgCodeBtn"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">text</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>leftS <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token number">0</span> <span class="token operator">?</span> <span class="token string">"5"</span> <span class="token operator">:</span> leftS<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"秒后重新获取"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>                <span class="token comment">//如果停止了倒数, 直接将按钮文本替换为重新获取, 并移除"on"样式</span>                <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"#msgCodeBtn"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">removeClass</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"on"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>                <span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"#msgCodeBtn"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">text</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"重新获取"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>            <span class="token punctuation">}</span>        <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
